<h3>Faulty Items</h3>
<p>If any product we supply fails prematurely due to a manufacturing defect we will provide you with a refund, replacement or repair. Simply call us on 08452 702 011 and we will arrange everything for you. Please ensure that you inform us of any damage to goods at the time of receiving them as soon as possible to avoid any delays in receiving a replacement or refund.</p>

<h3>Cancelling an order</h3>
<p>If you wish to cancel please inform us by email quoting your order number at <a href="mailto:enquiries@milletsports.co.uk">enquiries@milletsports.co.uk</a>. </p>
<h3>What if I have received my parcel, but they were not the goods ordered?</h3>
<p>Mistakes are rare, but they do happen. In the unlikely event that we have sent you the incorrect goods, then first of all we apologise. We want to make sure that we rectify this as soon as possible and ensure that we get the goods you ordered to you. In this event, please contact Customer Services by email <a href="mailto:enquiries@milletsports.co.uk">enquiries@milletsports.co.uk</a> where one of our advisors will be happy to assist you. They will email/send you a free returns label, which means you will be able to send the parcel back to us without incurring any postage costs. Please note it is our policy not to reimburse any postage costs as we provide this free service, and will always instruct our customers to use it. Customers must always send back their order with an accompanying returns form - this will ensure we can process your return quickly.</p>

